%20tax%20pro%20to%20help%20with%20my%202024%20return.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20selected%20a%20professional%20to%20work%20with%2C%20there%20was%20only%20one%20appointment%20left.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20a%20new%20business%20owner%2C%20I'm%20glad%20I%20worked%20with%20a%20pro%2C%20but%20the%20process%20was%20still%20stressful.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20last-minute%20tax%20filer%20%E2%80%94%20always%20have%20been%20and%2C%20despite%20my%20desire%20to%20change%2C%20likely%20always%20will%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%2C%20around%20mid-April%2C%20I%20scour%20my%20inbox%20for%20W-2s%20and%201099s%20and%20scramble%20to%20upload%20the%20correct%20documents%20to%20TurboTax.%20I%20submit%2C%20typically%20on%20deadline%20day%2C%20and%20cross%20my%20fingers.%20%3Cem%3EDid%20I%20forget%20anything%3F%20Fill%20something%20out%20wrong%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%2010%20years%20of%20self-filing%2C%20I%20haven't%20yet%20been%20audited%20%E2%80%94%20though%2C%20if%20the%20streak%20were%20to%20end%2C%20tax%20year%202024%20would%20be%20the%20year.%20I%20filed%20for%20an%20LLC%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-it-takes-lessons-launching-ecommerce-business-amazon-pickleball-paddles-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estarted%20an%20e-commerce%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202024%2C%20and%20knew%20I'd%20be%20in%20over%20my%20head%20from%20a%20tax%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20wanting%20to%20take%20any%20chances%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20hire%20a%20professional%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20The%20peace%20of%20mind%20and%20reduced%20stress%20would%20be%20worth%20the%20still-to-be-determined%20price%2C%20which%2C%20according%20to%20a%20quick%20Google%20search%2C%20could%20range%20anywhere%20from%20a%20couple%20hundred%20dollars%20to%20over%20%241%2C000%20for%20a%20small-business%20owner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20write%20this%20on%20the%20afternoon%20of%20April%2014%2C%20my%20taxes%20still%20aren't%20filed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20process%20has%20been%20just%20as%20stressful%20and%20more%20time-consuming%20as%20in%20previous%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20documented%20my%20tax%20filing%20journey%2C%20which%20began%20in%20mid-March%20when%20I%20started%20reaching%20out%20to%20professionals%20and%20culminated%20in%20a%20virtual%20appointment%20the%20day%20before%20the%20April%2015%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215bcc20d-2b88-444d-b7dd-f7b991271aae%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFinding%20a%20tax%20professional%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20more%20time%20looking%20for%20a%20tax%20preparer%20than%20I%20did%20uploading%20documents%20and%20meeting%20with%20the%20professional%20I%20eventually%20hired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdmittedly%2C%20I%20started%20the%20search%20process%20late.%20%26quot%3BHire%20an%20accountant%26quot%3B%20sat%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20to-do%20list%20for%20months.%20Part%20of%20the%20problem%20was%20that%20I%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20start.%20Plus%2C%20April%20felt%20like%20a%20lifetime%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20mid-March%2C%20the%20deadline%20effect%20started%20to%20kick%20in.%20I%20typed%20into%20Google%3A%20%3Cem%3EHow%20to%20find%20an%20accountant.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20helpful%20article%20recommended%20that%20I%20narrow%20my%20search%20to%20tax%20professionals%20specializing%20in%20small%20businesses.%20Yelp%20further%20narrowed%20my%20search%2C%20and%20I%20contacted%20three%20firms%20with%20strong%20reviews.%20By%20that%20time%2C%20it%20was%20late%20March.%20One%20firm%20didn't%20respond%2C%20one%20didn't%20have%20appointment%20availability%20until%20April%2022%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20I%20would%20have%20to%20file%20for%20an%20extension%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20quoted%20me%20%241%2C120%20after%20I%20filled%20out%20a%20short%20questionnaire%20via%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20relieved%20knowing%20that%20I%20at%20least%20had%20a%20%241%2C120%20option.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20felt%20pricey.%20I%20hoped%20a%20refund%20would%20cover%20some%20or%20all%20of%20it%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20concept%20of%20how%20much%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20I'd%20be%20getting%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wondered%2C%20%3Cem%3EIs%20this%20a%20negotiable%20service%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20helped%20me%20craft%20a%20response%20email%20to%20find%20out.%20We%20asked%20if%20they%20could%20reduce%20the%20fee%20by%20%24100%2C%20which%20the%20firm%20agreed%20to.%20Before%20committing%2C%20I%20called%20my%20mom%2C%20who%20owns%20a%20small%20business%20in%20North%20Carolina%2C%20to%20ask%20how%20much%20she%20pays%20her%20tax%20preparer%3A%20%3Cem%3E%24450%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20she%20told%20me.%20Our%20situations%20are%20different%2C%20and%20I%20live%20in%20California%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20help%20wondering%20if%20I%20could've%20asked%20for%20more%20of%20a%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20conversation%20prompted%20me%20to%20initiate%20one%20final%20search%2C%20which%20led%20me%20to%20a%20family%20business%20in%20southeast%20LA%20with%20nearly%20100%20five-star%20Yelp%20reviews.%20According%20to%20the%20prices%20listed%20on%20the%20website%2C%20it%20would%20be%20much%20more%20affordable%3A%20%24120%20for%20their%20W-2%20service%20and%20%24280%20for%20their%20single-member%20LLC%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20appointment%20remaining%20before%20tax%20day%3A%20April%2014%20at%209%20a.m.%20PT.%20I%20snagged%20it%2C%20knowing%20I%20could%20cancel%20if%20I%20went%20the%20pricier%20route%2C%20and%20weighed%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%3A%20I%20could%20save%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%2C%20but%20wouldn't%20have%20much%20room%20for%20error.%20If%20anything%20went%20wrong%20on%20the%2014th%2C%20I'd%20be%20scrambling%20to%20file%20an%20extension%20and%20estimate%20my%20tax%20liability.%20(While%20an%20extension%20extends%20your%20deadline%20to%20file%2C%20it%20does%20not%20extend%20your%20deadline%20to%20pay.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20roll%20the%20dice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b59943a-f310-473d-83b6-05ada157e3a1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreparing%20the%20tax%20return%20on%20April%2014%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20booked%20the%20appointment%20online%2C%20I%20received%20a%20text%20message%20confirming%20the%20meeting.%20A%20two-hour%20block%20also%20appeared%20on%20my%20Google%20calendar.%20A%20week%20before%20my%20appointment%2C%20I%20called%20to%20ask%20how%20to%20prepare%20and%20to%20confirm%20that%20a%20virtual%20meeting%20would%20suffice%2C%20as%20I'd%20be%20in%20New%20York%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20office%20told%20me%20I%20could%20start%20uploading%20documents%20to%20their%20portal%2C%20including%20copies%20of%20two%20different%20forms%20of%20identification%20and%20any%20applicable%20tax%20forms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20turned%20to%20ChatGPT%20once%20again%2C%20asking%20it%20to%20list%20specific%20documents%20I'd%20need%20to%20gather%20ahead%20of%20filing%20my%20taxes.%20Seconds%20later%2C%20it%20responded%20with%20a%20thorough%20checklist%20broken%20down%20by%20category%3A%20personal%20information%2C%20W-2%20employment%2C%20single-member%20LLC%2C%20and%20deductions%20and%20credits.%20It%20recommended%20I%20gather%20business%20expenses%2C%20which%20I%20had%20plenty%20of%2C%20and%20records%20of%20all%20sales%2C%20which%20I%20had%20none%20to%20report%20for%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221436%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22chatgpt%20screenshot%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feba213fe8d39283632570%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22818%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChatGPT%20helped%20compile%20a%20comprehensive%20list%20of%20items%20to%20gather%20for%20my%20tax%20pro.%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%20via%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2014%2C%20I%20eagerly%20awaited%20a%20call%20from%20the%20tax%20preparer's%20office.%20It%20came%20a%20few%20minutes%20after%209%20a.m.%20PT%20and%20would%20be%20the%20first%20of%20three%20mini-meetings%20over%20the%20phone.%20We%20exchanged%20pleasantries%2C%20and%20he%20asked%20a%20few%20questions%20about%20my%20business.%20He%20also%20asked%20how%20often%20I%20work%20in%20New%20York.%20That's%20when%20I%20remembered%20that%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance-money-investing-goals-after-move-to-new-york-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elived%20in%20New%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20one%20month%20(January)%20in%202024%20before%20moving%20to%20LA%20in%20February.%20That%20meant%20my%20W-2%20form%20was%20split%20into%20two%20and%2C%20while%20he%20typically%20does%20not%20prepare%20NY%20state%20tax%20returns%2C%20he%20said%20he%20could%20make%20an%20exception%3B%20it%20would%20just%20require%20more%20work%2C%20which%20I%20figured%20translated%20to%20a%20higher%20fee.%20This%20is%20also%20when%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20likely%20had%20another%20W-2%20from%20a%20part-time%20job%20I'd%20worked%20while%20living%20in%20NYC.%20Sure%20enough%2C%20a%20quick%20email%20search%20revealed%20a%20near-forgotten%20W-2%20showing%20about%20%241%2C000%20in%20wages%20for%20tax%20year%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20tax%20pro%20called%20me%20back%20about%20an%20hour%20later%20to%20ask%20a%20few%20more%20questions%2C%20mostly%20about%20the%20business.%20He%20alerted%20me%20of%20the%20LLC%20franchise%20fee%20I%20owed%20to%20California%2C%20explained%20that%20he'd%20be%20filling%20out%20a%20Schedule%20C%20to%20report%20my%20business%20losses%2C%20and%20offered%20some%20general%20best%20practice%20recommendations%20to%20make%20next%20year's%20filing%20as%20smooth%20as%20possible.%20I%20also%20told%20him%20I%20added%20another%20W-2%20to%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%2030%20minutes%20later%2C%20he%20called%20back%20to%20review%20my%20return.%20He%20explained%20that%20I'd%20be%20receiving%20a%20refund%20from%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20the%20state%20of%20New%20York%20and%20that%20I%20owed%20the%20state%20of%20California.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20look%20out%20for%20an%20email%20from%20him%20with%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20final%20return%2C%20which%20I%20would%20review%20and%20sign%20so%20he%20could%20e-file%20on%20my%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20came%20in%20a%20few%20hours%20later%2C%20as%20the%20workday%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%20was%20coming%20to%20a%20close.%20The%20one%20error%20I%20noticed%20was%20that%20my%20old%20address%20was%20listed%20on%20the%20return%20(my%20fault%2C%20as%20the%20copy%20of%20my%20ID%20that%20I%20provided%20wasn't%20yet%20updated%20with%20my%20new%20address).%20I%20scrolled%20through%20the%20rest%20of%20the%2022-page%20document%2C%20not%20entirely%20sure%20what%20else%20to%20look%20out%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20updated%20return%20with%20the%20correct%20address%20was%20waiting%20for%20me%20in%20my%20inbox%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20April%2015.%20I%20e-signed%20it%20right%20away%2C%20granting%20my%20tax%20pro%20permission%20to%20e-file%2C%20and%20emailed%20him%20asking%20about%20the%20next%20steps.%20Hoping%20to%20wrap%20things%20up%20before%20flying%20back%20to%20the%20West%20Coast%20that%20evening%2C%20I%20refreshed%20my%20inbox%20obsessively%20until%20I%20couldn't%20take%20it%20anymore%20and%20called%20the%20office%20for%20an%20update%20around%203%3A30%20p.m.%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20took%20down%20my%20information%20and%20promised%20to%20call%20me%20back.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20left%20for%20the%20airport%20at%204%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20I%20still%20hadn't%20received%20an%20update%20%E2%80%94%20nor%20did%20I%20have%20an%20invoice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20called%20back%20at%206%3A15%20p.m.%20ET%20while%20at%20the%20airport%20and%20asked%20for%20payment%20options%2C%20assuming%20they%20couldn't%20file%20until%20I%20paid.%20The%20bill%20came%20out%20to%20%24280%2C%20which%20I%20paid%20via%20Venmo.%20Mid-flight%2C%20I%20received%20an%20email%20from%20my%20tax%20pro%20saying%20he%20would%20file%20shortly%20and%20to%20look%20out%20for%20an%20email%20from%20the%20IRS%20confirming%20my%20return%20had%20been%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20hired%20a%20professional%2C%20particularly%20to%20help%20with%20the%20Schedule%20C.%20But%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I'm%20still%20the%20one%20gathering%20and%20uploading%20the%20documents%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20still%20crossing%20my%20fingers%2C%20hoping%20I%20didn't%20miss%20anything%20and%20hoping%20that%20the%20return%20was%20filed%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffile-taxes-how-much-cost-hire-tax-professional-worth-it-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744810059000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67feb5f1c6ad288d147e3a57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffile-taxes-how-much-cost-hire-tax-professional-worth-it-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20new%20business%20owner%2C%20I'm%20glad%20I%20hired%20a%20tax%20pro%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20make%20the%20filing%20process%20any%20less%20stressful.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffile-taxes-how-much-cost-hire-tax-professional-worth-it-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20don't%20know%20how%20you%20couldn't%20be%20embarrassed'%3A%20Wall%20Street%20is%20rethinking%20its%20Trump%20bet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Traders%20work%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f956d8c6ad288d147df5af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22784%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENEW%20YORK%2C%20NEW%20YORK%20-%20APRIL%2010%3A%20Traders%20work%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%2