r.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20mass%20transportation%2C%20it%20doesn't%20get%20easier%20than%20boarding%20a%20train.%20There%20are%20no%20security%20checkpoints%2C%20and%20I've%20rarely%20experienced%20lines.%20You%20should%20have%20no%20issues%20as%20long%20as%20you%20give%20yourself%20enough%20time%20to%20find%20the%20track%20your%20train%20departs%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20board%20overnight%20trains%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I%20typically%20arrive%20between%2015%20and%2030%20minutes%20before%20departure.%20In%20European%20cities%2C%20where%20stations%20are%20often%20larger%20and%20the%20language%20is%20different%2C%20I%20give%20myself%20a%20full%20hour%20to%20figure%20out%20where%20I%20need%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBoarding%20a%20cruise%20ship%20takes%20hours.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20line%20up%20to%20board%20a%20ship%20at%20a%20cruise%20ship%20terminal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f433ccc6ad288d147d74b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20line%20to%20board%20Wonder%20of%20the%20Seas.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20embarking%20on%20both%20cruises%2C%20I%20spent%20hours%20in%20line%2C%20and%20for%20good%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20their%20luggage%20had%20to%20load%20into%20a%20massive%20vessel%20safely%20and%20securely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20deny%20that%20I%20dread%20this%20part%20of%20a%20cruise%20as%20much%20as%20I%20dread%20going%20to%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETrain%20accommodations%20are%20tiny%20and%20typically%20lack%20a%20bathroom.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20inside%20of%20an%20Amtrak%20train%20roomette%20and%20a%20historic%20cabin%20on%20the%