e%2C%20and%20a%20full%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Royal%20Caribbean%20cabin%20had%20a%20window%2C%20and%20my%20Virgin%20Voyages%20room%20had%20a%20balcony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20not%20much%20to%20do%20on%20a%20train%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20that's%20kind%20of%20the%20point.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20sits%20reading%20in%20a%20train%20cabin%20with%20a%20window%20on%20the%20left%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6797c844eb4be2fff9a23e73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20reads%20on%20a%20train.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpace%20is%20very%20limited%20on%20trains%2C%20and%20there's%20not%20much%20to%20do%20on%20board.%20Exploring%20the%20train%20cars%20can%20be%20fun%2C%20and%20some%20trains%20have%20observation%20cars%20with%20massive%20windows%20for%20sightseeing.%20You%20can%20also%20get%20some%20fresh%20air%20during%20train%20stops%20that%20are%2010%20minutes%20or%20longer.%20But%20you'll%20likely%20spend%20most%20of%20your%20time%20in%20your%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20sound%20boring%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20a%20long%20train%20ride%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20be%20still%20for%20a%20while.%20When%20I%20spend%20my%20days%20exploring%20destinations%2C%20nights%20on%20trains%20force%20me%20to%20pause%20and%20relax%20without%20worrying%20about%20the%20time.%20I%20often%20take%20this%20time%20to%20catch%20up%20on%20reading%2C%20watch%20a%20movie%2C%20or%20listen%20to%20a%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20could%20easily%20entertain%20yourself%20all%20week%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222846%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22world's%20largest%20cruise%20ship%20wonder%20of%20the%20seas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f57650a466d2b74ab2941b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoyal%20Caribbean's%20Wonder%20of%20the%20Seas.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20most%20of%20a%20cruise%20is%20spent%20on%20a%20ship%2C%20it's%20no%20wonder%20cruise%20lines%20fill%20them%20with%20pools%2C%20sports%2C%20fitness%20centers%2C%20and%20activities%2C%20from%20gaming%20to%20dancing%20and%20live%20entertainment.%20The%20amount%20of%20things%20to%20do%20will%20vary%20depending%20on%20what%20size%20ship%20you%20choose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20board%20Royal%20Caribbean's%20Wonder%20of%20the%20Seas%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20cruise%20ships%20in%20the%20world%2C%20there%20were%20seemingly%20endless%20activities%20and%20unique%20offerings%20like%20laser%20tag%2C%20ice%20skating%2C%20and%20an%20escape%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Virgin%20Voyages%20cruise%20was%20on%20a%20midsize%20ship%2C%20but%20there%20was%20still%20plenty%20to%20do.%20My%20favorite%20part%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvirgin-voyages-adults-only-cruise-ship-playground-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadult%20playground%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20jumbo-sized%20swings%20and%20seesaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETrains%20generally%20have%20limited%20food%20options.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20two%20arieal%20shots%20of%20train%20meals%3A%20a%20lobster%20appetizer%20and%20a%20steak%20entree%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f57fb9c6ad288d147d93bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDishes%20on%20the%20Venice%20Simplon-Orient-Express%20(L)%20and%20Amtrak%20(R)%20trains.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I've%20had%20decent%20meals%20on%20overnight%20trains.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20train%20menus%20only%20have%20a%20few%20options%20per%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20noticed%20that%20Amtrak%20train%20food%20has%20improved%20over%20the%20years.%20Most%20recently%2C%20in%20January%202025%2C%20I%20particularly%20enjoyed%20a%20grilled%20chicken%20Caesar%20salad%20for%20lunch%20and%20a%20steak%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20board%20the%20luxurious%20Venice%20Simplon-Orient-Express%2C%20I%20had%20amazing%20fine-dining%20experiences%2C%20from%20eggs%20topped%20with%20caviar%20to%20scallops%20and%20lobster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECruises%20typically%20offer%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20food.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20line%20up%20and%20take%20food%20from%20a%20buffet%20on%20the%20left%20with%20an%20empty%20table%20on%20the%20right%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cf93d2397a16897202486d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20buffet%20aboard%20Wonder%20of%20the%20Seas.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20activities%2C%20the%20number%20of%20food%20options%20on%20cruises%20varies%20depending%20on%20ship%20size%2C%20but%20both%20ships%20I%20sailed%20on%20spoiled%20me%20by%20satisfying%20every%20craving.%20From%20buffets%20to%20restaurants%2C%20I%20could%20have%20Southern%20comfort%20food%20for%20breakfast%2C%20pasta%20for%20lunch%2C%20and%20Korean%20barbecue%20for%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETrain%20views%20are%20constantly%20changing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20A%20navy%20blue%20train%20with%20gold%20lettering%20moving%20in%20front%20of%20a%20body%20of%20water%20and%20mountains%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f578c1c6ad288d147d9244%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EViews%20from%20the%20Venice%20Simplon-Orient-Express.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20memorable%20views%20I've%20had%20were%20on%20trains.%20From%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%20to%20the%20Italian%20countryside%2C%20there's%20something%20romantic%20about%20gazing%20out%20the%20window%20from%20a%20train%20bunk%20at%20an%20ever-changing%20view%20of%20the%20world%20around%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20fascinating%20to%20watch%20the%20landscape%20transform%20throughout%20a%20trip.%20I'll%20never%20forget%20watching%20snowy%20mountains%20in%20Colorado%20melt%20into%20streams%20and%20canyons%20in%20Utah%20by%20sunset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECruise%20views%20are%20epic%20but%20often%20the%20same.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22And%20empty%20top%20deck%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship%20at%20sunrise%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F625efc11d2039d0019ba6389%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESunrise%20on%20a%20cruise%20ship.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20day%20one%20of%20a%20cruise%2C%20I'm%20amazed%20by%20the%20view%20of%20the%20open%20ocean.%20Sunsets%20at%20sea%20are%20unforgettable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trip%2C%20I%20don't%20stop%20to%20appreciate%20the%20view%20as%20much.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20because%2C%20aside%20from%20port%20stops%20and%20occasional%20islands%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20the%20views%20from%20a%20cruise%20ship%20typically%20stay%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETraveling%20by%20train%20is%20more%20sustainable%20than%20cruising.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223413%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Amtrak%20Superliner%20train%20parked%20in%20the%20snow%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f68d9dc6ad288d147da75e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrain%20travel%20has%20a%20lower%20carbon%20footprint%20than%20cruising.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20travel%2C%20I%20try%20to%20minimize%20my%20environmental%20impact%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20trains%20are%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-travel-more-sustainably-without-harming-destinations-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emost%20sustainable%20forms%20of%20transportation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Amtrak%20trips%20have%20a%20lower%20carbon%20footprint%20than%20flying%20or%20driving%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amtrak.com%2Fsustainable-travel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20company's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheicct.org%2Fmarine-cruising-flying-may22%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Council%20on%20Clean%20Transportation%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20cruise%20ships%20produce%20more%20carbon%20emissions%20than%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202025%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.transportenvironment.org%2Fstate-of-european-transport%2Fstate-of-transport-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEuropean%20Federation%20for%20Transport%20and%20Environment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ships%20accounted%20for%2012.7%25%20of%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20in%20Europe%20in%202024%2C%20while%20trains%20accounted%20for%200.4%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECruises%20may%20be%20more%20comfortable%2C%20but%20train%20trips%20leave%20me%20feeling%20more%20fulfilled.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20stands%20on%20a%20platform%20in%20front%20of%20a%20navy%20blue%20train%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a23880ec98e92f74f30f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20prepares%20to%20board%20an%20overnight%20train%20in%20Europe.%3Cp%3EJoey%20