g%20for%20new%20talent%20as%20it%20ramps%20up%20its%20data%20center%20ambitions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDozens%20of%20open%20roles%20related%20to%20AI%20infrastructure%20are%20listed%20on%20the%20startup's%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20comes%20as%20OpenAI%20starts%20to%20operate%20more%20independently%20of%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20OpenAI%20lessens%20its%20reliance%20on%20Microsoft%2C%20the%20AI%20startup%20is%20looking%20to%20add%20workers%20with%20data%20center%20experience%20to%20its%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20roughly%20300%20job%20listings%20on%20OpenAI's%20website%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20Business%20Insider%20counted%20more%20than%2020%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20directly%20related%20to%20data%20center%20development.%20Many%20of%20the%20open%20jobs%20involve%20building%20out%20the%20digital%20infrastructure%20that%20supports%20OpenAI's%20technology%20as%20the%20company%20uses%20more%20computing%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20infrastructure%20hiring%20push%20comes%20as%20the%20company%20starts%20to%20operate%20more%20independently%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ai-data-center-cloud-decreased-spending-explained-why-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20had%20until%20recently%20served%20as%20OpenAI's%20exclusive%20cloud%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-chatgpt-openai-ceo-career-net-worth-ycombinator-prepper-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20about%20the%20company's%20hiring%20push%20in%20an%20X%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fsama%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20interested%20in%20infrastructure%20and%20very%20large-scale%20computing%20systems%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20what's%20happening%20at%20OpenAI%20right%2