0being%20more%20drawn%20to%20the%20international%20section%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%20international%20relations%20at%20St.%20Andrews%20University%2C%20she%20%26quot%3Bwent%20from%20a%20very%20small%20team%20to%20the%20largest%20bureaucracy%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20first%20in%20operations%20and%20business%20development%20jobs%20at%20two%20startups%2C%20then%20to%20the%20Pentagon%20in%20policy%20and%20operations%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20Stockton%20worked%20for%20the%20Assistant%20Secretary%20of%20Defense%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20US%20industrial%20base%20could%20deliver%20capabilities%20warfighters%20need%20%E2%80%94%20a%20role%20she%20assumed%20only%20six%20months%20after%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine.%20%26quot%3BIt%20kind%20of%20felt%20like%20the%20broader%20world%20was%20waking%20up%20to%20how%20our%20manufacturing%20capacity%20has%20really%20shifted%20over%20the%20last%20three%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20this%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20with%20both%20incumbent%20defense%20companies%20and%20emerging%20players%20reignited%20her%20interest%20in%20the%20startup%20ecosystem.%20At%20Overlap%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20combine%20her%20D.C.%20and%20operational%20expertise%20to%20help%20startups%20interpret%20how%20policy%20changes%20affect%20their%20business%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decisions%20that%20are%20made%20in%20Washington%20impact%20companies%20day%20in%20and%20day%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Stockton%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20need%20to%20expand%20our%20domestic%20capacity%20across%20all%20these%20frontier%20technology%20companies%20only%20remains%20more%20urgent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStockton%20won't%20be%20investing%20at%20Overlap.%20Instead%2C%20she'll%20work%20with%20startups%20directly%2C%20offering%20them%20tailored%20guidance%20on%20which%20grants%20or%20contracts%20best%20suit%20their%20stage%2C%20sector%2C%20and%20product.%20She%20will%20also%2