%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20Asked%20Parents%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20One%2090s%20Summer%20Memory%20You%E2%80%99re%20Recreating%20With%20Your%20Kids%20Today%3F%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20grew%20up%20in%20India%20in%20the%2090s%2C%20you%20know%20that%20summer%20truly%20began%20when%20school%20ended%20for%20the%20year.%20There%20were%20no%20alarms%2C%20just%20sunlit%20mornings%2C%20cousins%20pouring%20in%2C%20and%20the%20comforting%20whirl%20of%20the%20ceiling%20fan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99d%20spend%20hours%20on%20the%20terrace%20or%20outdoors%2C%20our%20fingers%20stained%20purple%20from%20peeling%20jamuns%2C%20laughing%20over%20nothing%20and%20everything.%20Family%20cricket%20matches%2C%20marbles%2C%20hopscotch%20chalked%20onto%20the%20driveway%20%E2%80%94%20our%20calendars%20were%20ruled%20by%20the%20sun%2C%20not%20the%20clock.%20And%20somehow%2C%20even%20the%20boredom%20felt%20like%20a%20gift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20parents%2C%20we%20often%20find%20ourselves%20asking%2C%20can%20our%20kids%20ever%20experience%20summers%20the%20way%20we%20did%3F%20With%20screens%20everywhere%20and%20schedules%20packed%2C%20it%20feels%20harder%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20took%20my%20five-year-old%20daughter%20to%20the%20Goa%20Science%20Centre%20in%20Miramar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20quiet%2C%20breezy%20spot%20with%20hands-on%20exhibits%2C%20a%20mini%20planetarium%2C%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343042%2Fias-vivek-johnson-establishes-open-science-parks-sports-complexes-for-rural-children-transforms-chandrapur-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%2